						<li>Reproduction, distribution or modification of content without prior authorization is not permitted</li>
						<li>The user is responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of any information provided</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section class="mb-8">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">3. Intellectual and Industrial Property</h2>
					<p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
						The design, source code, logos, texts, graphics, images, icons, as well as the structure and design of this website, are the property of Ignacio Amat or third parties who have authorized their use, and are protected by intellectual and industrial property rights.
