					</p>
				</section>

				<section class="mb-8">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">7. Personal Data Protection</h2>
					<p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
						The processing of personal data is carried out in accordance with the Privacy Policy, which forms an integral part of this Legal Notice. For more information on how we process your personal data, please see our <a href="/en/privacy" class="text-accent hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a>.
